{{Infobox Berry |name = Figy |image = [[File:Figy.png]] |caption = This Berry is oddly shaped, appearing as if someone took a bite out of it. It is packed full of spicy substances. |growtime = 5m 50s |harvest = 14 berries |replant = 30% |points = 40 |flavor = {{!}} 15 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 }} '''Figy''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding an empty plot with at least 25, but no more than 80 points of spicy and less than 5 points of all other flavours. The [[Cheri]] must be unlocked to unlock this berry.
